{"tid":1365331,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗美食推介","createTime":"2019-07-25T15:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T15:33:06.000Z","uid":289991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7988367c4efb7226e7f730b2f789639bd0569a36","tid":1365331,"uid":289991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:12:53.000Z","msg":"元朗是吃貨的天堂。這10家是我搬元朗後，親身試過而且會encore的真心推介。畢竟只搬過來1年，還有很多很多美食還未試，未能盡錄。<br />\n<br />\n**本人沒有各食肆店舖的背景資料，請自行搜查，多謝<br />\n<br />\n1. 車仔麵 - 永年士多<br />\r\n完美評價：食車仔麵我最重視舊蘿蔔。蘿蔔做得入味，其他餸都不會太差。湯底鮮味不太咸，麵質也爽口。<br />\n網址: <a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0F3S000~u4j4HAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0F3S000~u4j4HAA&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=00f7cd6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0F3S000~u4j4HAA</a><br />\r\n地址: 元朗教育路88號寶城洋樓地舖2-4號<br />\r\n電話: 24773816<br />\n<br />\n2. 雞飯 - 過橋麵檔<br />\r\n完美評價：不是食過橋米線，而是食霸王雞菜飯。雞肉滑，炸蒜和香蔥極極香，配上微甜豉油，本身不喜歡食蔥的我也清碟了。燉湯也很甜，但只有冬天才有。<br />\n網址: <a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0Ya8000~u4j4HAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0Ya8000~u4j4HAA&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=630139d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0Ya8000~u4j4HAA</a><br />\r\n地址: 元朗建德街25號大福中心地下1號舖<br />\r\n電話: 24494810<br />\n\r<br />\n3. 燉蛋 - 蘇記流心燉蛋專門店<br />\r\n完美評價：米芝連推介，採用日本富良野牛奶。起滑超濃奶味。注意，3時後才開檔<br />\n網址: <a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS02HS800~u4j4HAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS02HS800~u4j4HAA&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=a70353ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS02HS800~u4j4HAA</a><br />\r\n地址: 元朗鳳攸東街9號好順意大廈A座地下15號舖<br />\r\n電話: 90729135<br />\r\n<br />\n4. 香辣雞翼尖、涼粉 - 佳記甜品<br />\r\n完美評價：B仔涼粉出名，但其實最正是雞翼尖。辣香有種令人「追住食」的魔力。<br />\n網址: <a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0O0O000~u4j4HAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0O0O000~u4j4HAA&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=e69567a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0O0O000~u4j4HAA</a><br />\r\n地址: 元朗教育路大坑渠側<br />\r\n電話: 24733148<br />\r\n<br />\n5. 老婆餅 - 恆香老餅家<br />\r\n完美評價：不多解釋，老婆餅我只買這家。每次出城探親戚朋友都會買一盒做手信。<br />\n網址: <a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0H28000~u4j4HAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0H28000~u4j4HAA&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=f1ecc3c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0H28000~u4j4HAA</a><br />\r\n地址: 元朗青山公路64號地下<br />\r\n電話: 24763080<br />\r\n<br />\n6. 雞蛋仔 - The Waffle Club<br />\r\n完美評價：論脆口比不上媽咪雞蛋仔，但這家的雞蛋仔味濃。裡面是比較充實的蛋漿造成，而不是空心的。粉紅包裝加心心形雞蛋仔，加上店舖裝修靚，影相打卡位呀。<br />\n網址: <a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0BUW800~u4j4HAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0BUW800~u4j4HAA&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=137b49a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0BUW800~u4j4HAA</a><br />\r\n地址: 元朗西菁街2號興旺樓地下1C號舖<br />\r\n電話: 28864508<br />\r\n<br />\n7. 台灣牛肉麵 - 士林台灣麵<br />\r\n完美評價：在香港食到好味的台灣麵很難。這家跟台灣的相比，起碼有8-9成似。無論是湯底或是牛肉都做得比較正宗。<br />\n網址: <a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0E3e000~u4j4HAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0E3e000~u4j4HAA&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=ffb4b611\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0E3e000~u4j4HAA</a><br />\r\n地址: 元朗西菁街9號富盛大廈地下<br />\r\n電話: 24779775<br />\r\n<br />\n8. 乳鴿、雞粥 - 新記煲仔雞粥<br />\r\n完美評價：食過多家乳鴿，這家最好。貴妃雞粥是第二推介。<br />\n網址: <a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0IbK000~u4j4HAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0IbK000~u4j4HAA&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=9ad96d27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0IbK000~u4j4HAA</a><br />\r\n地址: 元朗又新街42號D2地舖<br />\r\n電話: 24425129<br />\r\n<br />\n9. 酒香雞湯米 - 澳門街水蟹粥雞湯米<br />\r\n完美評價：大排檔，酒香撲鼻。雞湯甜而濃厚。<br />\n網址: <a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0sFe700~u4j4HAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0sFe700~u4j4HAA&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=dd508ef9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0sFe700~u4j4HAA</a><br />\r\n地址: 元朗鳳攸南街3號好順景大廈地下2座地下18號舖<br />\r\n電話: 24556888<br />\n<br />\n10. 蝦子麵 - 好到底麵家<br />\n完美評價：老字號，米芝連推介。多蝦子，麵質爽口。可買麵餅做手信。<br />\r\n網址: <a href=\"https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0F1i000~u4j4HAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.openrice.com%2FQrbS0F1i000~u4j4HAA&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=78f6573d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.openrice.com/QrbS0F1i000~u4j4HAA</a><br />\r\n地址: 元朗阜財街67號地舖<br />\r\n電話: 24762495<br />\r\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/340492413377231/posts/478435302916274?s=665673358&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F340492413377231%2Fposts%2F478435302916274%3Fs%3D665673358%26sfns%3Dmo&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=2b882cff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/340492413377231/posts/478435302916274?s=665673358&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"731a365227df5f7ff5e47a45ca657a05f80bea63","tid":1365331,"uid":289991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}